{"tid":2099111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港經濟係好難大跌 外資都係睇錢 唔係睇政治","createTime":"2020-07-08T04:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T04:47:10.000Z","uid":84408,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"46191b8d50f64b64369420b7b403c4eaa3710497","tid":2099111,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:04:43.000Z","msg":"當然黃圈係一個比較成功將資金流入本地市場嘅好例子<br />\n但無可否認<br />\n每年都係極大量嘅錢仲係響外資／中資手中<br />\n<br />\n要打經濟制裁真係好難<br />\n另外中共見到外國聯手制佢老味<br />\n一定會縮手先<br />\n起碼唔係極大規模咁起集中營或將香港變第三世界咁<br />\n因為香港仲有最基本嘅價值<br />\n<br />\n但其實我地時間係真心無乜<br />\n如果再唔繼續起新野 改經濟模式等等<br />\n<br />\n隔幾年外國見到香港情況「穩定」後<br />\n支持度就會下降<br />\n<br />\n到時中共必定再出手<br />\n居安思危<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc6071c7aa3e7a6a75101269aef30324d7a5bc5","tid":2099111,"uid":51057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"又會咁岩2個po痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAaXAGb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAaXAGb.png&h=a5edd4e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35e929727eed483a0623432eb5b63c0185b7aaf7","tid":2099111,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8dc6071c7aa3e7a6a75101269aef30324d7a5bc5","tid":2099111,"uid":51057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:15:06.000Z","msg":"又會咁岩2個po痴埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAaXAGb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAaXAGb.png&h=a5edd4e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:24:39.000Z","msg":"我指嘅係過多一段日子<br />\n當連登唔再係講移民嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a9d55909d017c69900fb031b11c2a1a5dde2b2","tid"